    <h1>HARO</h1>
    <p class="description">A platform connecting journalists with expert sources for stories — used by SEOs to earn <strong>editorial backlinks from DA 70+ publications</strong> at zero cost. Requires speed, genuine expertise, and quotable answers to win placements.</p>
